+
* *indian_creek.bil* http://ogrip.oit.ohio.gov/ProjectsInitiatives/StatewideImagery.aspx[State of Ohio] LiDAR data (http://coast.noaa.gov/inventory/[obtained via NOAA interagency data site]) from Indian Creek, Ohio. ENVI bil format, projected into WGS84 UTM zone 11N.
