* *WhiteadderDEM.tif* http://catalogue.ceda.ac.uk/uuid/8f6e1598372c058f07b0aeac2442366d[Taxpayer funded, yet commercially liscenced] https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Interferometric_synthetic_aperture_radar[IfSAR data] 5m data from Whitadder cathcment, Scotlan. GeoTiff format, projected in the British National Grid.
